   \frac{2 \cot(t) }{ \cot(t) + \tan(t) } = \frac{2 \frac{\cos(t)}{\sin(t)} }{ \frac{\cos(t)}{\sin(t)} + \frac{\sin(t)}{\cos(t)} } = \frac{2 \cos^2(t)}{ \cos^2(t) + \sin^2(t) } = 2 \cos^2(t) . 
